            <title>苹果 watchOS 10.3 正式发布：加速应用启动、修复耗电过快、提升系统性能</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/746/668.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/746/668.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:08:10 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2326146" rel="nofollow">快乐小刺猬</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 1 月 23 日消息，苹果今日向 Apple Watch 用户推送了 watchOS 10.3 更新（内部版本号：21S644），本次更新距离上次发布隔了 48 天。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="苹果 watchOS 操作系统" height="461" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2022/4/8bd386fb-ecc7-474d-bd95-4c69ba122e7a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEzOC5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_14,x_14,a_0/format,f_auto" title="苹果 watchOS 10.3 正式发布：加速应用启动、修复耗电过快、提升系统性能" width="900" /></p><p>需要注意的是，因苹果各区域节点服务器配置缓存问题，可能有些地方探测到升级更新的时间略有延迟，一般半小时内，不会太久。</p><p>苹果公司今天面向 Apple Watch 发布了 watchOS 10.3，本次更新重点在于<strong>改善性能、修复错误，以及引入新的辅助功能。</strong></p><p>IT之家附上 watchOS 10.3 主要改进如下：</p><h3>提升性能和稳定性：</h3><p>watchOS 10.3 应该会让你的 Apple Watch 感觉更快、反应更灵敏。据报道，应用程序的启动时间更快，整体系统性能也有所提升。</p><h3>更快的应用程序启动时间：</h3><p>现在，您在 Apple Watch 上启动最喜欢的应用程序的速度应该比以前更快了。</p><h3>解决耗电过快问题：</h3><p>一些用户在更新到 watchOS 10.2 后报告了电池耗尽问题，苹果声称已在 watchOS 10.3 中修复了这些问题。</p><h3>新的无障碍功能：</h3><p>watchOS 10.3 包含新的无障碍功能，如语音控制改进和手表表面的新音频描述。</p><h3>修复：</h3><p>苹果在 watchOS 10.3 中修复了一系列与表盘和复杂功能相关的错误。</p><h3>附 watchOS 10 发布历史：</h3><ul class="custom_reference list-paddingleft-1"><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/745/840.htm" target="_blank">2024-01-18：watchOS 10.3 Release Candidate (21S644)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/744/286.htm" target="_blank">2024-01-10：watchOS 10.3 Beta 3 (21S5642a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/743/234.htm" target="_blank">2024-01-04：watchOS 10.3 Beta 2 (21S5635d)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/738/852.htm" target="_blank">2023-12-13：watchOS 10.3 Beta (21S5625c)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/737/367.htm" target="_blank">2023-12-06：watchOS 10.2 Release Candidate (21S364)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/735/703.htm" target="_blank">2023-11-29：watchOS 10.2 Beta 4 (21S5358a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/732/576.htm" target="_blank">2023-11-15：watchOS 10.2 Beta 3 (21S5349e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/731/426.htm" target="_blank">2023-11-10：watchOS 10.2 Beta 2 (21S5342e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/730/806.htm" target="_blank">2023-11-08：watchOS 10.1.1 (21S71)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/727/950.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-27：watchOS 10.2 Beta (21S6331f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/725/620.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-11：watchOS 10.1 Release Candidate (21S67)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/724/056.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-11：watchOS 10.1 Beta 3 (21S5063a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/722/968.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-04：watchOS 10.1 Beta 2 (21S5053f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/722/168.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-28：watchOS 10.1 Beta (21S5042f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/721/890.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-27：watchOS 